                            <comment id="14439084" author="wsmoak" created="Wed, 5 Mar 2008 20:40:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Vincent, you marked this for 2.4 back in January.  Are you planning to work on it, or should we bump it to 2.5?  I&apos;d like to stage 2.4 this weekend.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14439083" author="bentmann" created="Sat, 8 Mar 2008 07:23:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch attached. The logic has been extended to accept &quot;&amp;lt;snip&amp;gt;/javadoc&quot; on all platforms by appending &quot;.exe&quot; automatically on Windows boxes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Besides the fix, I made the parameter accept a mere directory spec, too, as a matter of convenience.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
